// ItemCard
// Card component for displaying a session item (diagram, design, document,
// spreadsheet, snippet) in the sidebar item list.

FUNCTION formatRelativeTime(ts) -> string
  Just now, Xm ago, Xh ago, Xd ago, or locale date string.

---

FUNCTION detectLanguage(fileName) -> string
  Maps file extensions to human-readable language names (TypeScript, Python, etc.)

---

FUNCTION getSnippetMetadata(content) -> SnippetMeta
  Parses JSON envelope to extract code, language, filePath.
  Counts lines. Formats size in B/KB/MB.

---

FUNCTION getItemIcon(type) -> JSX
  Returns an appropriate SVG icon for diagram/design/spreadsheet/snippet/document.

---

FUNCTION ItemCard(item, isSelected, onDelete, ...) -> JSX              EXPORT
  Renders item name, type label, relative time, and optional snippet metadata.
  Delete button appears on group-hover (CSS group-hover pattern).
  IF snippet: shows language, line count, and file size via getSnippetMetadata.
  snippetMetadata is memoized.
